Hi Tushar

I have been reviewing the Critical ticket logged for your StealthAUDIT report issue.

As I understand there is an issue with a custom job running, however you are unfamiliar with this job.

As this is Critical it is important you have a clear definition of what the issue is so we can progress this.

It is pertinent we understand who created the custom job so we can work with that relevant team. Without this progress will be very difficult to reverse engineer the custom work.

Please provide examples of what is not working, screenshots of the relevant jobs, clear examples of any data discrepencies.

Following this you can use the following link to schedule a meeting with me. I currently have time available in 90minutes from now which can be selected in this link:

https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=DWICQIBzT1pz0BMopwRqhg3BMnbITxocGgeROsN5l_s-Z&MeetingID=hw4Mu7qdka3guQOt7Uav1evs.4uh_JLpBgQ4M8CaW_k-Z
